https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

This directory contains MAMUT-routing conversions, repairs, metadata, and
computed BKS records for the static VRPTW layer of the EURO Meets NeurIPS 2022
Vehicle Routing Competition. Those derived benchmark artifacts are distributed
with the ORTEC family under the same CC BY-NC 4.0 notice unless an individual
file states otherwise.

The MIT license in the repository root applies to MAMUT-routing source code,
not to these ORTEC benchmark data files.
